  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">Scenario 1 (TL;DR): `tldr: string[]` renders as semantic `<ul>` with `<li>` children; no raw JSON tokens; evidence screenshot captured.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Scenario 2 (Entities): `entities: { organizations, persons }` renders as labeled blocks with nested bulleted lists; no raw JSON object literal; evidence screenshot captured.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Scenario 3 (Dedup): typing `/summarize` produces ONE rendered output; server logs show ONE LLM call + ONE playbook execution + ONE DeliverOutput + ONE render. Both slash and natural-language entry paths verified.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Scenario 4 (Matter pre-fill): ZERO drift vs task 034 AFTER baseline; per-field wizard outputs identical; latency within ±10%; NFR-07 binding honored.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Scenario 5 (Project pre-fill): ZERO drift vs task 035 AFTER baseline; per-field wizard outputs identical; latency within ±10%; NFR-07 binding honored.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Scenario 6 (Backward compat): action with NULL `sprk_outputschemajson` renders as string (legacy); no crash; no error.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Evidence file `notes/task-048-phase-b-integration-evidence.md` exists with screenshot/log/diff references per scenario.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Server log excerpts captured per ADR-015 — tool names + decisions + timestamps ONLY; no user message text.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">BFF publish-size delta = 0 MB (confirmed in evidence notes; no BFF code changed by this task).</criterion>
